{"type":null,"faqId":33543,"title":"手机界面显示语音信箱是怎么回事？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>语音信息的内容是保持在运营商服务器上的，用户要收听该语音信息，需要回拨语音信息号码才能收听，接听后该提示才会彻底消失。如果没有接听而被用户不小心清楚，那将漏掉语音信息。给用户造成不良影响。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>解决方法：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>一、按着“新语音邮件”选项向左或者向右滑动，将会弹出如下框。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>二、点击“确定”，则清除系统栏中的新语音信息提醒。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>注：重启后系统栏会再次提示，用户需要按照上述方法重新操作一遍。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果用户需要收听语音信息，请按如下步骤操作：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>拨打运营商客服电话（如：中国移动10086）查询本地对应的语音信箱号码。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>“通话设置”选择“语音信箱设置”。同时在下一个界面选择“语音信箱号码”。输入运营商所告知的本地语音信箱号码即可。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8263","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748651000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":8,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"语音信箱","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}